snippet.title: Dog Gone Golfing - PS4 Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Dog Gone Golfing is now available on Playstation 4.

https://store.playstation.com/en-ca/product/UP1701-CUSA12793_00-0000111122223333
www.vagabonddog.com/gone-golfing

Choose your power, pick your shot type, and plan your approach as you slap and bounce your puck towards each hole. Play your angles just right and you could become the legendary Canine Puck Master. Do you have enough skill to avoid space meteors, lava fireballs, and rotten gophers?
